This paper is about improving image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning models (cs.LG) and data-driven approaches (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of concept-level annotations to improve performance, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
